And Daryl Lane

24:26.020 --> 24:27.460
Brian Aldiss' latest

24:27.460 --> 24:28.640
Science Fiction novel

24:28.640 --> 24:29.560
Is the masterful

24:29.560 --> 24:30.560
Achievement of an author

24:30.560 --> 24:31.300
Who is at the height

24:31.300 --> 24:32.560
Of his very awesome powers

24:32.560 --> 24:33.560
It's called

24:33.560 --> 24:34.460
Helliconia Spring

24:34.460 --> 24:35.640
And it's the first volume

24:35.640 --> 24:36.200
Of a trilogy

24:36.200 --> 24:37.320
About an Earth-like planet

24:37.320 --> 24:38.200
Called Helliconia

24:38.200 --> 24:39.400
Aldiss tells us

24:39.400 --> 24:40.080
About the planet

24:40.080 --> 24:40.920
And the books

24:42.460 --> 24:42.980
Helliconia

24:42.980 --> 24:44.760
Is the name

24:44.760 --> 24:45.360
Of a planet

24:45.360 --> 24:46.320
That's really

24:46.320 --> 24:47.420
Much like Earth

24:47.420 --> 24:48.980
And a lot of

24:48.980 --> 24:49.780
Earth-like things

24:49.780 --> 24:50.560
Go on there

24:51.380 --> 24:52.140
But

24:53.200 --> 24:54.280
It is

24:54.280 --> 24:55.400
The child

24:55.400 --> 24:57.540
Of binary suns

24:58.340 --> 25:00.140
And it takes

25:00.140 --> 25:02.000
Two and a half thousand years

25:02.000 --> 25:03.320
To go round

25:03.320 --> 25:04.360
The primary

25:04.360 --> 25:06.180
I mean

25:06.180 --> 25:07.900
Two and a half thousand

25:07.900 --> 25:08.760
Earth years

25:11.500 --> 25:13.160
Which is to say

25:13.160 --> 25:14.380
That between

25:14.380 --> 25:15.560
One winter

25:15.560 --> 25:16.260
And the next

25:17.280 --> 25:18.420
You can have

25:18.420 --> 25:18.960
A whole lot

25:18.960 --> 25:19.920
Of civilizations

25:19.920 --> 25:21.640
Doing a whole lot

25:21.640 --> 25:22.960
Of declining

25:22.960 --> 25:23.720
And falling

25:24.740 --> 25:26.120
And of course

25:26.120 --> 25:27.860
Falling and rising

25:28.680 --> 25:30.340
And so that

25:30.340 --> 25:32.780
These three long volumes

25:32.780 --> 25:34.880
Really just cover

25:34.880 --> 25:36.760
Parts of

25:36.760 --> 25:38.100
One of Helliconia's

25:38.100 --> 25:38.880
Great years

25:39.880 --> 25:41.160
So there's

25:41.160 --> 25:41.960
At once

25:41.960 --> 25:44.140
This marvelous

25:44.140 --> 25:45.000
Continuity

25:45.000 --> 25:46.520
As I see it

25:46.520 --> 25:48.140
Of one year

25:48.140 --> 25:49.660
And yet

25:49.660 --> 25:51.080
Of many generations

25:51.080 --> 25:52.180
And many cultures

25:53.980 --> 25:55.080
And that's

25:55.080 --> 25:56.040
The basic plan

25:56.040 --> 25:56.640
Of the book

25:56.640 --> 25:58.380
They're simply titled

25:58.380 --> 25:59.160
The first one

25:59.160 --> 26:00.280
Is Helliconia Spring

26:00.280 --> 26:00.900
That's the one

26:00.900 --> 26:01.480
That's out

26:01.480 --> 26:02.600
The one I'm writing

26:02.600 --> 26:03.860
Is Helliconia Summer

26:05.480 --> 26:06.860
And after that

26:06.860 --> 26:07.500
I go on

26:07.500 --> 26:08.560
To Helliconia Winter

26:09.680 --> 26:10.680
After centuries

26:10.680 --> 26:11.680
Of a deadening winter

26:11.680 --> 26:12.680
Spring is coming

26:12.680 --> 26:13.380
To Helliconia

26:13.380 --> 26:14.400
And the primitive

26:14.400 --> 26:15.080
Men of the planet

26:15.080 --> 26:15.720
Are waking up

26:15.720 --> 26:16.180
To the greater

26:16.180 --> 26:17.400
Possibilities of life

26:17.400 --> 26:18.880
To higher aspirations

26:18.880 --> 26:19.560
And knowledge

26:19.560 --> 26:20.600
To the construction

26:20.600 --> 26:21.620
Of a new civilization

26:21.620 --> 26:23.140
The first volume

26:23.140 --> 26:23.960
Traces the life

26:23.960 --> 26:24.880
Of a nomadic hunter

26:24.880 --> 26:25.640
Named Yuli

26:25.640 --> 26:26.720
And his descendants

26:27.440 --> 26:28.840
Because the first volume

26:28.840 --> 26:29.840
Is about the sun

26:29.840 --> 26:30.820
Bursting out

26:32.120 --> 26:33.720
The first volume

26:33.720 --> 26:34.640
Is just stacked

26:34.640 --> 26:35.540
Full of things

26:35.540 --> 26:36.480
Bursting out

26:36.480 --> 26:37.700
And people

26:37.700 --> 26:38.600
Bursting out

26:38.600 --> 26:39.280
Animals

26:39.280 --> 26:40.160
Bursting out

26:41.500 --> 26:42.460
It's a great

26:42.460 --> 26:43.580
Bursting out novel

26:51.380 --> 26:52.600
Circling Helliconia

26:52.600 --> 26:53.160
Is a satellite

26:53.160 --> 26:53.740
From Earth

26:53.740 --> 26:54.980
A huge observation

26:54.980 --> 26:55.380
Station

26:55.380 --> 26:56.180
Which monitors

26:56.180 --> 26:57.100
Everything that happens

26:57.100 --> 26:57.780
In Helliconia

26:57.780 --> 26:58.700
And beams it to Earth

26:58.700 --> 27:00.520
Aldiss spent a painstaking

27:00.520 --> 27:01.760
Four years on the book

27:01.760 --> 27:03.160
Striving for accuracy

27:03.160 --> 27:03.840
And realism

27:05.140 --> 27:06.340
Well I hope people

27:06.340 --> 27:07.480
Will find that it's

27:08.180 --> 27:09.820
Full of reality

27:10.560 --> 27:11.640
That's why I say

27:11.640 --> 27:12.460
The moral of it

27:12.460 --> 27:12.960
Should be

27:12.960 --> 27:14.300
Mere existence

27:14.860 --> 27:15.840
Because I think

27:15.840 --> 27:16.420
They recognize

27:16.420 --> 27:17.600
Their own lives

27:18.740 --> 27:19.940
Passing through the book

27:20.920 --> 27:23.120
And the other motive

27:23.120 --> 27:23.880
I had

27:23.880 --> 27:24.860
Was that

27:26.280 --> 27:28.720
I grew rather alarmed

27:28.720 --> 27:29.260
At the way

27:29.260 --> 27:30.880
So much science fiction

27:32.480 --> 27:34.080
Since it's become

27:34.080 --> 27:35.940
More popular

27:35.940 --> 27:38.280
Has been full of

27:39.260 --> 27:40.740
What shall we say

27:40.740 --> 27:41.860
Fantasy

27:41.860 --> 27:43.080
Wish fulfillment

27:43.080 --> 27:45.220
I didn't like that

27:45.220 --> 27:46.100
I think that

27:46.100 --> 27:47.120
Science fiction

27:47.120 --> 27:49.360
Should reflect

27:50.400 --> 27:52.580
The facts of life

27:53.680 --> 27:55.860
The hard facts of life

27:55.860 --> 27:58.180
It shouldn't just be

27:58.180 --> 28:00.000
Some nonsense about

28:00.000 --> 28:02.300
One guy against

28:02.300 --> 28:03.580
A malign empire

28:03.580 --> 28:04.660
Who goes out

28:04.660 --> 28:06.600
And you know

28:06.600 --> 28:08.040
Kills the chief baddie

28:08.760 --> 28:09.880
I thought it should

28:09.880 --> 28:10.500
Have a little more

28:10.500 --> 28:11.980
Contact for reality

28:11.980 --> 28:13.480
And moreover

28:13.480 --> 28:15.380
I'll sound old fashioned

28:15.380 --> 28:16.420
If I say this

28:16.420 --> 28:17.580
But I think

28:17.580 --> 28:18.660
That sort of thing

28:18.660 --> 28:20.040
Is better

28:20.040 --> 28:21.360
For the nation's

28:21.360 --> 28:21.840
Youth

28:21.840 --> 28:23.280
Than the old

28:23.280 --> 28:24.420
Hogwash about

28:25.460 --> 28:26.480
Telepathic dragons

28:26.480 --> 28:27.680
And all the rest of it

28:34.760 --> 28:35.600
Helliconia Spring

28:35.600 --> 28:36.360
Is a remarkable

28:36.360 --> 28:37.300
And unique achievement

28:37.300 --> 28:38.260
By a man who is not

28:38.260 --> 28:38.780
Just a great

28:38.780 --> 28:39.680
Science fiction writer

28:39.680 --> 28:40.540
But one of the

28:40.540 --> 28:41.120
Finest writers

28:41.120 --> 28:41.760
Of our time

